Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必自責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你充其量人類而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放跑了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來猜對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主人公得知戀人死亡的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,take five
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一週？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官長時間不在沒問題麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去有些事情搞不定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時老實享受學校生活罷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 做個好學生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cut cut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的集 感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他光明正大地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說變了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定在大島上有過什麼事呢	
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南島假日 盛夏冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是少年登上大人的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的 人生不如意事十之八九呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了設施 說他沒出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去常在一起玩的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失物在水族館？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失物又不是魚來著吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 戀愛的幸運物是虎紋水壺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？哪兒有那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎紋水壺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆還沒回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是櫻滿的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯太攝影在用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人的遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說總而言之讓祈帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 東西忘在社團室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你帶過去好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地你陪祭買東西去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…花音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油 好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說有幽靈出沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大島研究所裡有人用櫻滿黑周博士的ID進出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼解釋麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿博士過去的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莖道修一郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 哪站下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西…有很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿得下不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集…我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 歡樂麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 谷尋同學 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋 沒別的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡全盤托出？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭 買東西拜託你一人去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話和谷尋說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿集同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視你是正確的選擇吶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說要銷毀潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們趁亂逃了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為心想不能繼續留潤在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出賣你得到的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻逃了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又摔了下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有哪兒疼？潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 潤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到在逃的病源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}捕捉到在逃的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Cancer{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 勁爆地漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區捉個病源 真需要我的Endrave？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}區區捉個{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Cancer{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100} 真需要我的Endrave？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吶 boy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常言道龍擊敗史萊姆時也會盡全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍吃史萊姆麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 刀疤臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩勁爆mission clear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處世之道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能…借錢不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃命 吃飯都需要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為借錢才特地給我看潤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託集 保護得了潤的人…除了我沒別人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想請你們保護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒患者 病源已經開始惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Apocalypse Virus{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}患者 病源已經開始惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 等我聯絡四分儀再給你指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起我們趕往黃一點 拜託一小時候後接頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有原諒你的作為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤沒罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好 馬上就會用上它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌已經不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 潤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一小會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出洞了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基因捕捉的準備如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為啥用它？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了解戀愛對象不可以麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請動手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗體？為啥這麼快被發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Anti-Bodies{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}？為啥這麼快被發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早料到了 現在快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會又是葬儀社的人來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺明是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騰出逃生路徑 誘敵出洞是基本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種外行人的思考會要人命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才要做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}我有{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人類心靈抽取成武器的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能打倒Endrave
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信那種話？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的人不是你叫來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破偽善者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會像你一樣出賣同伴 見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證帶潤逃跑 說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋閉上嘴乖乖給我用！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 又是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破聲控仔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤 我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天的是特制啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西會追著那光走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 那麼連發如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 噓界！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可著實有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西和天啟病源呈現相同反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常動作？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！沒事吧？潤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼和谷尋交代…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒導致機器發生了基因共鳴麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Apocalypse Virus{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}導致機器發生了基因共鳴麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在那裡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reboot Bin！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部輸入！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓界少校 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰終止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…六本木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落聖誕前夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}LOST X'MAS{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}前夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…潤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於說上話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別禮物喲 是你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2029年十二月二十四日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最幸福的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落聖誕即將爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}LOST X'MAS{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}即將爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想懷抱著唯一的幸福回憶 啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 用那個虛空剪斷我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}集 用那個{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}剪斷我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的虛空是斬斷生命的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}哥哥的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void  {\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}是斬斷生命的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}  Void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我送葬的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}為我送葬的{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有…此理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結晶剝奪走我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地給了我看得見虛空的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}相對地給了我看得見{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}Void{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒有另一個哥哥 和他在我面前表現的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃匹薩噢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的西紅柿匹薩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥買給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看過無數個善者的惡面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 親戚大嬸 醫療中心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半集…你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續活下去 又將經歷無數次痛苦的輪回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會討厭哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走下去 保持住喜歡哥哥的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落聖誕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&Hff&}{\alpha&H00&\fscx60\fscy60}LOST X'MAS{\alpha&Hff&\fscx100\fscy100}！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好怕 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 有哥哥在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠 永遠在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 這樣下去我會殺死哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 有我在是累贅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毀了哥哥的人生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破哥哥啊 我也…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生不如意事十之八九呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 潤…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
